metadata.name: curiosity
metadata.description:
December 29, 2022.

Anniversary of the Fall of Daten Io.

Her name is Daten Io.

She has a free-spirited personality and does not like boring days.

In the heavenly realm, there is little stimulation because everything is fulfilled.

In the heavenly realm, there is no greed, no resentment, no jealousy, no joy, and everyone seems to be a saint.

She longs for the view of the earth from the heavenly world. Humans are fashionable, jealous, happy, angry, sad, joyful, contentious, and lively every day.

So she voluntarily decides to fall to the earth.

When she fell, she also forced two angels to come with her. Those two resisted badly. They were out of control of IO, so now I carry them around as hair ornaments.

From today onward, I will enjoy the earth.
